# Interactive Modules Guide

Interactive modules are shortcodes that provide user interaction in articles.

## Resource Links Module

Location: [layouts/shortcodes/interactive-modules/resource-links.html](mdc:layouts/shortcodes/interactive-modules/resource-links.html)

Displays curated external resources with descriptions.

```hugo
{{< interactive-modules/resource-links title="Further Resources" columns="2" description="Explore these trusted sources" >}}
  {{< interactive-modules/resource-card title="Resource Title" url="https://example.com" type="tool" >}}
    Description of the resource.
  {{< /interactive-modules/resource-card >}}
  
  {{< interactive-modules/resource-card title="Another Resource" url="https://example.com/article" type="article" >}}
    Description of another resource.
  {{< /interactive-modules/resource-card >}}
{{< /interactive-modules/resource-links >}}
```

Parameters for resource-links:
- `title`: Section title (default: "Useful Resources")
- `columns`: Number of columns - "1", "2", or "3" (default: "2")
- `description`: Optional description text

Parameters for resource-card:
- `title`: Resource title (required)
- `url`: Resource URL (required)
- `icon`: Optional icon
- `type`: Resource type - "article", "video", "tool", or "guide" (default: "article")

## Condition Checklist Module

Location: [layouts/shortcodes/interactive-modules/condition-checklist.html](mdc:layouts/shortcodes/interactive-modules/condition-checklist.html)

Interactive tool for assessing item condition with scoring.

```hugo
{{< interactive-modules/condition-checklist title="Condition Assessment Tool" description="Check all items that apply to estimate condition rating" >}}
  {{< interactive-modules/checklist-item label="Item is fully functional" >}}
    Detailed description of what this means.
  {{< /interactive-modules/checklist-item >}}
  
  {{< interactive-modules/checklist-item label="No visible damage or wear" >}}
    Detailed description of what to look for.
  {{< /interactive-modules/checklist-item >}}
{{< /interactive-modules/condition-checklist >}}
```

Parameters for condition-checklist:
- `title`: Section title (default: "Condition Assessment Checklist")
- `description`: Optional description text

Parameters for checklist-item:
- `label`: Item description (required)
- `weight`: Relative importance weight (default: "1")

## Auction Results Module

Location: [layouts/shortcodes/auction-results.html](mdc:layouts/shortcodes/auction-results.html)

Displays notable auction sales in a structured format.

```hugo
{{< auction-results title="Notable Auction Results" description="Recent high-value sales" >}}
  {{< auction-item item="Antique Watch" price="$40,000" date="June 2024" auctionHouse="Christie's" >}}
  {{< auction-item item="Vintage Camera" price="$3,200" date="May 2024" auctionHouse="eBay" >}}
{{< /auction-results >}}
```

Parameters for auction-results:
- `title`: Section title (default: "Auction Results")
- `description`: Optional description text

Parameters for auction-item:
- `item`: Item name or description (required)
- `price`: Sale price (required)
- `date`: Sale date (required)
- `auctionHouse`: Name of auction house or platform (required)
